 on Dua: Etiquette of order for supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while Abu Bakr and Umar were with him. When I sat down, I began by praising Allah, then sending blessings upon the Prophet, then supplicating for myself. The Prophet said, \u201cAsk and you will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-salat-ala-al-nabi-most\/","url_meta":{"origin":11578,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Nearest to Prophet blessed him most","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe closest of people to me on the Day of Resurrection are those who sent the most blessings upon me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 484 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14615,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/06\/dua-tashahhud-allah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":11578,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Supplication at the end of sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard a man supplicating in his prayer, and he did not send blessing upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cThis man has rushed.\u201d Then, the Prophet called for the man or some others, and he said, \u201cWhen one of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/allah-displeased-if-no-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11578,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah displeased with unmindful gatherings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit in a gathering without remembering Allah, or sending blessings upon their Prophet, but that they will earn the displeasure of Allah. If Allah wills, He will punish them. If He wills, He will forgive them.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19589,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/seven-five-takbir-salat-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":11578,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Seven and five Takbir in Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Awf reported: The Prophet, peace and blessi